    public abstract class AbstractCPN<P extends AbstractCPNPlace<F>,T extends AbstractCPNTransition<F>,F extends AbstractCPNFlowRelation<P,T>,M extends AbstractCPNMarking>
extends AbstractPetriNet<P,T,F,M,de.invation.code.toval.types.Multiset<java.lang.String>>
    Class for defining Colored Petri nets (CPNs), which are a special kind of Petri nets that consider distinguishable tokens (with different colors).

    The class defines specific markings that respect CPN properties.
    Markings contain for each place the number of tokens it contains for different colors. By providing appropriate methods, the class allows to add relations having constraints
    (which define the number of tokens transferred over the relation for different colors).
    作者:
    Thomas Stocker

      • addFiringRule

        public void addFiringRule(java.lang.String transitionName,
                          FiringRule rule)
        Adds a firing rule for a transition to the Petri net.
        A firing rule of a transition defines the tokens needed to fire (to get enabled) for places leading to the transitions and the tokens that are produced and added to places connected with outgoing relations.
        This method translates the given firing rule into constraints for incoming and outgoing relations of the given transition and sets them accordingly.
        参数:
        transitionName - The name of the transition for which the firing rule is added.
        rule - The firing rule.
        抛出:
        de.invation.code.toval.validate.ParameterException - If some parameters are null, the transition is unknown
        or the firing rule contains unknown places.

      • fireCheck

        public M fireCheck(java.lang.String transitionName)
            throws PNException
        从类复制的说明: AbstractPetriNet
        Returns the marking which is the result of firing the transition with the given name.
        The transition is not actually fired, but its firing impact with respect to the actual net state
        simulated and returned in form of a resulting marking.
        指定者:
        fireCheck 在类中 AbstractPetriNet<P extends AbstractCPNPlace<F>,T extends AbstractCPNTransition<F>,F extends AbstractCPNFlowRelation<P,T>,M extends AbstractCPNMarking,de.invation.code.toval.types.Multiset<java.lang.String>>
        参数:
        transitionName - The name of the transition to fire.
        返回:
        true if the transition could be fired;
        false otherwise.
        抛出:
